This repository contains my personal study notes used while preparing for and passing the CompTIA A+ certification exams (Core 1 & Core 2).
These notes were created while reading the Mike Meyers All-in-One CompTIA A+ Certification Exam Guide (11th Edition) and are organized chapter by chapter to reflect my actual learning process.
The goal of this repo is to:

- Reinforce my own understanding
- Demonstrate consistent study habits to employers
- Help other beginners navigate A+ topics more confidently

